About Us

Welcome to Fruiter, your ultimate destination for fresh and high-quality fruits delivered right to your doorstep. Established with a passion for health and well-being, we strive to offer the finest selection of fruits that are not only delicious but also nutritious. Since our inception, we have been committed to providing exceptional service and maintaining the highest standards of quality.

Our Mission

At Fruiter, our mission is to make healthy living easy and accessible. We are dedicated to sourcing the freshest fruits and delivering them with care to our customers. We believe in the power of nature's goodness and aim to promote a healthier lifestyle through our products.

Our Team

  • Kamesh - Founder & CEO
  • Rohit Sharma - Head of Quality Control
  • Virat Kohli - Customer Service Manager
  • Jasprit Jasveersingh Bumrah - Operations Manager

Certifications

  • Organic Certification: Certified by APEDA gov of India for sourcing and selling organic fruits.
  • Quality Assurance: Recognized for maintaining high standards of quality and safety in fruit handling and distribution.
  • Sustainability Award: Awarded for our efforts in promoting sustainable practices in agriculture and packaging.

Our Values

  • Quality: We prioritize quality in everything we do, from selecting fruits to delivering them to your doorstep.
  • Customer Satisfaction: Your satisfaction is our priority. We are committed to providing exceptional service and ensuring your fruit-buying experience is enjoyable.
  • Health and Wellness: We promote a healthy lifestyle by offering nutritious fruits that contribute to your well-being.
  • Sustainability: We care about the environment and are committed to sustainable practices in our operations.
